@heading Version 2.00
@itemize
@item removed memory leaks
@item integrated Output class from Wendy
@item added make target "win32" to compile the api without linking against the cygwin1.dll
@item added manpage for petri tool
@item API can be compiled with foreign config.h (removed macro dependencies)
@item added scripts to use LCOV
  (`http://ltp.sourceforge.net/coverage/lcov.php') to determine test case
  coverage (use `make cover' in `tests' directory)
@item new features:
@itemize
@item Transition costs (https://gna.org/task/index.php?6615)
@item test cases and integration of new owfn parser (https://gna.org/task/index.php?6658)
@item Function to add a prefix to all places and transitions (https://gna.org/task/index.php?6749)
@item Integrate Genet for SA2ON conversion (https://gna.org/task/index.php?6767)
@end itemize
@item fixed bugs:
@itemize
@item PetriNet does not know Synchronous Labels of its transitions (https://gna.org/bugs/index.php?13936)
@item sa2sm/sa2owfn ignore synchronous labels (https://gna.org/bugs/index.php?13968)
@item Net reduction invalidates finalCondition and leads to core dump (https://gna.org/bugs/index.php?13969)
@item Composition of more than two nets fails because of prefixes to I/O places (https://gna.org/bugs/index.php?13990)
@item No (public) method to remove nodes (https://gna.org/bugs/index.php?14003)
@item Removal of dead nodes also deletes interface place (https://gna.org/bugs/index.php?14064)
@item Arc weights to/from interface places are ignored by isNormal() function (https://gna.org/bugs/index.php?14116)
@item Normalization yields unequivalent nets (https://gna.org/bugs/index.php?14119)
@item No error when using SYNCHRONIZE with undeclared label in oWFN file (https://gna.org/bugs/index.php?14127)
@item LoLA-Parser is more strict than LoLA's parser (https://gna.org/bugs/index.php?14206)
@item synchronous steps become tau-transitions (https://gna.org/bugs/index.php?14335)
@item product with constraint does not work with synchronous communication (https://gna.org/bugs/index.php?14411)
@item When composing nets, costs of a transition get lost (https://gna.org/bugs/index.php?14417)
@end itemize
@item further (undocumented) bugs fixed
@item further (undocumented) changes
@end itemize

